headline: Philip Morris U.S. launches national advertising campaign
summary: Daviess County residents are generally aware of the impact Swedish Match continues to have in the community, both through offering high-paying jobs and its charitable activities. But Philip Morris International’s U.S. business (PMI U.S.) — owner of Swedish Match — has launched a national advertising campaign to spread the word about and reinforce its commitment to U.S. manufacturing.
